      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey friends! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape and has been well-maintained over the years. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend road trips, this beauty still has plenty of life left and is looking for a great new home. Come take her for a spin\u2014you're going to love how she handles!",
