    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has been proactively maintained with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive rod bearing service. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, sending power through a variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry is enhanced by refreshed bushings and a focused alignment, ensuring the chassis remains neutral under lateral load. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain integrity and throttle response remain exceptionally crisp for the discerning driver.",
