      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for driver. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated deep metallic blue that still holds a brilliant shine, with only a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway commuting. Inside, the cabin remains smoke-free and remarkably clean; the leather upholstery is supple and free of rips, showing only light 'character lines' on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features, including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, boasting a consistent service history with oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. The transmission shifts smoothly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It recently passed a comprehensive safety inspection and sits on tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a turn-key car that has been maintained with an open checkbook, perfect for someone who wants quality without the 'new car' price tag.",
